data.description: Fantastic home in Fir Meadows is the perfect abode if you like to entertain. Open concept living on upper level with large bay window for plenty of natural light & propane fireplace warms vaulted great room. Kitchen boasts marbled island counter eating space with views of the private yard. A sizable primary suite offers vast closet space & en-suite bath. Comfortable floor plan with stylish laminate flooring, bonus living room, bedroom & full bath downstairs. From the level, fenced lot, garden beds, long driveway, Leaf Gutter system, RV parking, huge tiered deck & tree-lined backyard- This is a wonderful place to be! Oversized 2 car garage with shed for everything else. Ideal cul-de-sac location, ready for the next owner to make it their own
